{"id": "1249810574767034530", "channel_id": "1249810574767034530", "type": 0, "author_id": "1212784185639567390", "author_name": "kirot0150", "author_bot": false, "content": "直接化为死抗高手🤓\n\n\n1-3打的好不如抗的多，双暴造物有莉莉会很舒服，可惜我没有，只能爆死抗了\n\n\n2-3应该是比较简单的一关，深海或者旺达叠盾抗住就行，可以留在最后打，地图症状多，可以带消除症状的r卡。\n\n\n3-3最折磨的一集，没练宁妃，带上宁妃叠毒应该很轻松，24开了十几个大才磨死boss，注意boss多段技能就行\n\n\n4-3开五次大boss就会放大招还招小怪，油污现在就能很好的解决这个问题，而且油污不吃boss的封印，就很舒服，道中带上蜘蛛和神父可以很好的保证血量，boss关只需要开油污和羊妈大招就行\n\n5-3注意别在boss二阶段拖太久就行，艾继丝一阶段伤害不高而且给的迟缓也少，在一阶段生生胎，然后进二阶段红花一套秒就行。", "timestamp": "2024-06-10T19:41:01.382000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-10T19:41:50.564000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1249810575517810818", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-10-19-50-33-83_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 163533, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249810574767034530/1249810575517810818/Screenshot_2024-06-10-19-50-33-83_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=69cc234d&is=69cad1cd&hm=b3937a4b6c18f276751cf698089fb5e3685fb8796f638bf9b0808f5fbc193895&"}, {"id": "1249810575811149885", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-11-03-11-17-34_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 158335, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249810574767034530/1249810575811149885/Screenshot_2024-06-11-03-11-17-34_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=69cc234d&is=69cad1cd&hm=93ba9457aeaf267d607c786513f098cc07fc8636930c1277ec2165fcc0a3c45c&"}, {"id": "1249810576184709140", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-11-03-11-20-25_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 162458, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249810574767034530/1249810576184709140/Screenshot_2024-06-11-03-11-20-25_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=69cc234d&is=69cad1cd&hm=3aedf6ecd0438f0bb373d579a07afc104cd3c6531dfe5f90afd7ffed2471bb61&"}, {"id": "1249810576545284217", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-11-03-1